{"tid":2446140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國女子失蹤多周後屍體尋回　一名英國警員被控綁架及謀殺","createTime":"2021-03-14T08:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T05:15:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c4429c9884670f17be40dffae8c7851894f9f25b","tid":2446140,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427226&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=f5527c1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D427226&h=02e76408\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=427226</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】英國女子埃弗拉德在倫敦失蹤個多星期後，警方尋到她的屍體，一名警員被控綁架和謀殺，今日提堂。事件在當地引起哄動，關注女性在公眾場所的安全。<br />\n<br />\n英國警方證實，周三在東南部肯特郡阿什福德附近樹林發現的屍體，是失蹤33歲女子埃弗拉德<br />\n<br />\n埃弗拉德在倫敦南部居住，本月三日晚離開朋友寓所，獨自走路回家時半途失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n警方事後以涉嫌綁架和謀殺，拘捕在肯特郡居住的48歲警員卡曾斯，以及據報是他伴侶、涉嫌協助行兇的30多歲女子。<br />\n<br />\n卡曾斯2018年9月加入警隊，去年二月調職到國會與外交保護小隊，負責倫敦多處大使館的保安工作。<br />\n<br />\n而在埃弗拉德失蹤前幾天，曾有人報案指卡曾斯在快餐店露體，獨立監察部門正就倫敦大都會警察廳當時的處理手法展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n本案令英國女性人心惶惶，擔心在公眾場所的安全，疑兇的警員身份更令社會震驚。不少女性在社交網站分享自己的經歷，並在帖文標註「只不過是走路回家」。<br />\n<br />\n有民眾不滿警方早前歸咎女性獨自外出，將責任推在女性身上，亦有人在社交網站發起周六舉行悼念活動，但警方以新冠病毒防疫令為由不批准。<br />\n<br />\n內政大臣彭黛玲強調，會盡力保障婦女安全。<br />\n<br />\n首相約翰遜亦表示，明白公眾對女性安全的關注。約翰遜：「我完全明白為何本案會觸發廣泛的關切，有關女性的安全在街上的安全。」<br />\n<br />\n倫敦警方則承諾會加強巡邏。"},{"pid":"06439aeeee34e62668992cf38941205e036af3e9","tid":2446140,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"成件事有無姦殺，咁單純謀殺？<br />\n<br />\n簽名檔<br />\n==================================<br />\n[評論黃世澤幾分鐘] 分析下沈旭暉同黃世澤既分別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2441952/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2441952/page/1</a><br />\n[戇鳩警報器: 黃世澤| martin oei | 交加街38號] 警世黃世澤係令大家用唔到BNO移民既始作俑者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2423877/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2423877/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d0ecd519dcb1a425669ab6cde32af76403a4fc37","tid":2446140,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a131d454e5e796d7c0d3045596d871fb688843","tid":2446140,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aad6a49b88cfbc07e0c576e9d15f2eb656ee86","tid":2446140,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23a131d454e5e796d7c0d3045596d871fb688843","tid":2446140,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:57:16.000Z","msg":"天"},{"pid":"2a4a69ea299cb1a8746b2713bddbfae87b84e093","tid":2446140,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:51:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3eb8ec820c4ff45728f1e8bd2f11cbdb6f688f20","tid":2446140,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T01:52:55.000Z","msg":"蝧國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a427de70c18427b632a07f08c4ad52369fb4c34","tid":2446140,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"天下黑警一樣黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}